{"tid":2489041,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"C AllStar新歌《留下來的人》 送給香港人","createTime":"2021-04-14T16:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T00:57:24.000Z","uid":381856,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"00c7d515d24be87d214320001b80a550c0fa27a4","tid":2489041,"uid":381856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:03:21.000Z","msg":"詞曲都好正，聽完好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />串流平台應該啱啱上咗架<br />\n<br />\n曲：徐沛昕<br />\n詞：曰云<br />\n編：何秉舜<br />\n監：簡<br />\n<br />\n觀賞街景那動態 誰在半路停步<br />\n試聽著每顆心跳和脈膊起伏<br />\n拼了命成就幸福<br />\n世界在平衡著多少心痛 開始跟結束<br />\n<br />\n可呼吸多數萬次 難道這樣容易<br />\n你最後那一口氣呼了便化煙<br />\n為何明明在眼前 明明同行但你臨時別去 放下句點<br />\n<br />\n許多人都相信離開的人生走到該走的那時 痛著來話別<br />\n可知留低的與重生的 卻在這邊<br />\n怎撐過餘生的浩劫 （只可接受 新生活的蛻變）<br />\n<br />\n差不多三百日了 沉澱過又懷念<br />\n要記住你的一切 使世界亮了點<br />\n原來仍能活過來 仍能糊塗地愛悠然地笑 過著每天<br />\n<br />\n祈求站在世界的終端相擁嗎<br />\n還能如常還能再對話<br />\n若到那天 地球還未塌下<br />\n尚能期待某種永遠嗎<br />\n<br />\n幾多人不捨那離開的 誰都懂說生死都有時 降淚時 又如何避免<br />\n留低的與重生的 也在這邊<br />\n即使費時一點 即使快樂不輕易 最後仍可遇見"},{"pid":"839de336de9340aba5e8ba5ffda9cc81c07382dd","tid":2489041,"uid":62891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c5ee4922f577d1b9a4bafa71d3849f9764e0e9","tid":2489041,"uid":75487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:05:46.000Z","msg":"但我真的信香港明天會更好<br />\n#我賭的是無人殺我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e5b61f5ea79f7082e9442f720a9f3991f885b3","tid":2489041,"uid":245552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9990aec519ec5e83ef8176e1bf3f8738717e26","tid":2489041,"uid":89823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:12:56.000Z","msg":"推。好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32498b15fb5f77ecc738d2a6eab5fb778ed4f39","tid":2489041,"uid":389955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:13:43.000Z","msg":"等咗好耐 <br />\n2nd plug 繼續高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b056ec05e174d599214a319cf64579f8a484364c","tid":2489041,"uid":389955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:15:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.kkbox.com/hk/en/song/xBE00TK978NgxEOlgxEOl0XL-index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kkbox.com%2Fhk%2Fen%2Fsong%2FxBE00TK978NgxEOlgxEOl0XL-index.html&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=d9c17e2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kkbox.com/hk/en/song/xBE00TK978NgxEOlgxEOl0XL-index.html</a><br />\n<br />\nKkbox 已上架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd7ff6c4cecf74413b62a4b2d2358094d9cef11","tid":2489041,"uid":206809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:18:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bd495b0af841a5e356dd2af50a7225cf6bf9d3a","tid":2489041,"uid":219736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:29:29.000Z","msg":"即使費時一點 即使快樂不輕易 最後仍可遇見"},{"pid":"0b57221d5fd40487023474a784154bec2bcb70d1","tid":2489041,"uid":261006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:31:33.000Z","msg":"「離開了的<br />\n留下來的<br />\n總會有一天<br />\n在世界的另一邊<br />\n彼此集合，好好相見」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s